{
  "title": "ISic003640. Epitaph for Elpidephoros and Nike",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Γονεῦσιν γλυκυ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>τάτοις ζησάντοις <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἀμέμπτως πρὸς <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>πάντας φίλους ἐπό-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ησεν <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τρυφέρα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τρυφέρα\">Τρυφέρα</span></span> θυγά-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>τηρ ζήσαντι <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἐλπι\n                    δηφόρῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἐλπι\n                    δηφόρῳ\">Ἐλπι-<br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>δηφόρῳ</span></span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span> ἔτη ❦πε´ ❦ <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νίκῃ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νίκῃ\">Νίκῃ</span></span> ἔτη ❦ π´ ❦ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΓΟΝΕΥΣΙΝΓΛΥΚΥ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΤΑΤΟΙΣΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΙΣ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΜΕΜΠΤΩΣΠΡΟΣ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΠΑΝΤΑΣΦΙΛΟΥΣΕΠΟ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΗΣΕΝ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τρυφέρα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τρυφέρα\">ΤΡΥΦΕΡΑ</span></span>ΘΥΓΑ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΤΗΡΖΗΣΑΝΤΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἐλπι\n                    δηφόρῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἐλπι\n                    δηφόρῳ\">ΕΛΠΙ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΔΗΦΟΡΩ</span></span> &nbsp;&nbsp;ΕΤΗ❦ΠΕ❦<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νίκῃ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νίκῃ\">ΝΙΚΗ</span></span>ΕΤΗ❦Π❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003640_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\" src=\"ISic003640_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003640.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\" src=\"ISic003640-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text based upon photograph</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>For my dearest parents, who lived blamelessly towards all their friends. Tryphe, their daughter, made it, for Elpidephoros, who lived 85 years, and Nike who lived for 80 years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Manganaro 1965 199 tav.70.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Alpha with straight bar; lunate epsilon and sigma; uncial mu and omega; rhomboid omicron, theta and phi.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
